# LogTideTracker - Macro-Pattern Log Analyzer

LogTideTracker highlights long-term frequency waves and shifts in log behavior for large-scale applications.

## Features
- Frequency tide analysis  
- Heatmap visual summaries  
- CLI-based inspection

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LogTideTracker.git
cd LogTideTracker
python analyze.py
